                <h2>Typography</h2>
                <p>The best design is invisible; beautiful typesetting often is. Keep it simple and readable like the text in your favorite novel. Avoid using bold, italic, underline, highlights, size changes, bullets, numbering and any other method used to make content stand out more. Those typographic treatments can hinder the reader and add visual clutter to your future design.</p>
